kamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/26bb9fded79fbbd44929746aaac01e76.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/26bb9fded79fbbd44929746aaac01e76.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >我們該怎麼辦？</h2>你需要駕駛一輛豪華銀色哈弗，從維塔利的鄉村住宅偷偷逃走。<br>解鎖門鎖、砸開木板、打開配電箱、砸壞地板、扔碗盤，用嘈雜的聲音吸引維塔利的注意，並享受PS4時代的畫面效果！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/b1069e12f4492d7f3d4693fb7678b935.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/b1069e12f4492d7f3d4693fb7678b935.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/b1069e12f4492d7f3d4693fb7678b935.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >遊戲的主要特色：</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要逃離這個邪惡住宅的物品位置是隨機的！<br></li><li>一個神秘的追求者，無論你藏在哪裡，他都會追著你。<br></li><li>一個充滿魅力的女主角，讓人無法抗拒。<br></li><li>計劃有多個逃生路線。最終會實現的。<br></li><li>大量的彩蛋！<br></li><li>真正的鏡中反射！你上次看到這種效果是什麼時候？<br></li><li>你可以躲在馬桶裡。<br></li><li>變得成功又富有！</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/04cf35728824d4e6c6bf2b6f4c76b284.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/04cf35728824d4e6c6bf2b6f4c76b284.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/04cf35728824d4e6c6bf2b6f4c76b284.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><spa