90/extras/c8fdfd6b8c1b659640451694d20345ed.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Upon waking up, Maria realizes that Vitaly brought her to his place. But she’s not that kind of girl. So she firmly decides that she needs to escape at any cost...<br><strong>But for free!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/26bb9fded79fbbd44929746aaac01e76.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/26bb9fded79fbbd44929746aaac01e76.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/26bb9fded79fbbd44929746aaac01e76.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What we gonna do?</h2>You need to sneak away from Vitaly’s country residence in a luxurious silver Haval.<br>Unlock doors, break planks, open electrical panels, smash floors, throw dishes, distract Vitaly with loud noises, and enjoy PS4-era graphics!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/b1069e12f4492d7f3d4693fb7678b935.poster.avif?t=1766944259\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/b1069e12f4492d7f3d4693fb7678b935.webm?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144590/extras/b1069e12f4492d7f3d4693fb7678b935.mp4?t=1766944259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features of the Game:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Randomized placement of items needed to escape this evil residence!<br></li><li>A mysterious admi